pnpm store prune      # clean pnpm cache
pnpm store path       # pnpm store location

### npm to pnpm
rm -rf node_modules
[Optional] Create pnpm-workspace.yaml if you use workspaces
pnpm import
git rm package-lock.json
pnpm install
pnpm approve-builds  # approve all of them
add in package.json:
  "packageManager": "pnpm@10.30.3",
Replace all npm run xxx commands to pnpm run xxx
